tell me something about arrow function -


features of arrow function -

1)Concise Syntax:

2)Implicit Return:

Arrow functions automatically return the result of the expression without the need for an explicit return statement if the function body is a single statement. 

3)No Binding of this:

Arrow functions do not bind their own this value. Instead, they inherit the this value from the enclosing scope.

4)Shorter Syntax for Single-Parameter Functions:


